Evogene Advances Most in Two Months on Monsanto Agreement

-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 
2011-11-29T14:50:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-29/evogene-of-israel-soars-most-in-two-months-on-monsanto-agreement.html
Evogene Ltd. (EVGN)  rose the most in more
than two months after the developer of plant traits for the
agriculture and biofuel industries extended and expanded a
collaboration agreement with Monsanto Co.  The shares increased 5.5 percent, the biggest gain since
Sept. 26, to 14.96 shekels at the 4:30 p.m. close in  Tel Aviv .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  